"In :numref:`figure_floc_baffle_spacer_detail`, the washer is located "
"downstream of the polycarbonate baffle so that the force of the water on the"
" baffle is first transferred to the washer before being transferred to the "
"pipe spacer to reduce the forces applied near the hole through the baffle."
